  → predicted_trajectory + ci_trajectory on CooldownData
- cooldown_service.py:420-430 already publishes these arrays in metadata
- analytics_layout.yaml: cooldown phase → main = cooldown_prediction widget

### F-P2 — Vacuum leak projection overlay
STATUS: WIDGET EXISTS (VacuumPredictionWidget + PredictionWidget),
but DATA PATH NOT WIRED. Needs implementation.
Gap:
- VacuumPredictionWidget (analytics_widgets.py:403) expects set_vacuum_prediction(dict)
  with keys: history, central, lower, upper, ci_level_pct
- AnalyticsView.set_vacuum_prediction() exists but main_window_v2.py never calls it
- Engine has VacuumTrendPredictor publishing via ZMQ get_vacuum_trend (polled by
  legacy VacuumTrendPanel), but that data is not forwarded to AnalyticsView
Decision: Add poll timer + set_pressure_reading() buffer to VacuumPredictionWidget.
  Poll get_vacuum_trend, convert extrapolation_t/extrapolation_logP/residual_std
  → central/lower/upper (log₁₀P → mbar), accumulate raw pressure history
  via set_pressure_reading().
  Same self-contained pattern as VacuumTrendPanel (no main_window_v2 changes).

### F-P3 — TIM asymptote overlay
